---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | Prestige, Inc." description="Privacy Policy for Prestige, Inc. transportation and logistics communications.">
	<section class="bg-white py-20 text-brand-slate">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-10">
			<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-blue">Legal</p>
			<h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-brand-navy">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-slate-500">Last updated: May 18, 2026</p>

			<div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-base leading-8 text-slate-700">
				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-overview">
					<h2 id="privacy-overview" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Overview</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						Prestige, Inc. respects the privacy of customers, prospective customers, carriers, vendors, and website visitors. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, retain, and protect information submitted through our website, quote forms, shipment communications, and ordinary business interactions.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-information">
					<h2 id="privacy-information" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Information We Collect</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						We may collect contact details, company information, shipment details, communication preferences, billing or administrative information, and website usage information necessary to respond to quote requests, coordinate transportation services, support compliance, and maintain business records.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-use">
					<h2 id="privacy-use" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">How We Use Information</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						We use information to respond to inquiries, prepare quotes, coordinate shipments, communicate service updates, improve website performance, maintain security, satisfy legal obligations, and conduct internal business administration.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-sharing">
					<h2 id="privacy-sharing" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Information Sharing</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						We may share information with service providers, logistics partners, professional advisors, or government authorities when reasonably necessary to provide requested services, comply with law, protect rights, or operate our business. We do not sell personal information.
					</p>
					<p class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-brand-safety/40 bg-amber-50 p-5 font-semibold text-brand-slate">
						Mobile information will not be shared with third parties or affiliates for marketing or promotional purposes. All the above categories exclude text messaging originator opt-in data and consent; this information will not be shared with any third parties.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-security">
					<h2 id="privacy-security" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Data Security and Retention</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						We use administrative, technical, and organizational safeguards designed to protect information from unauthorized access, misuse, alteration, or disclosure. We retain information only as long as reasonably necessary for business, operational, compliance, and legal purposes.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section aria-labelledby="privacy-choices">
					<h2 id="privacy-choices" class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-navy">Your Choices</h2>
					<p class="mt-3">
						You may contact us to request updates to your information or to ask questions about this Privacy Policy. SMS recipients may opt out of text messages as described in our Terms of Service.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</BaseLayout>